 tim izrazov nije to bilo ni djete,

222
00:11:25,620 --> 00:11:26,500
 ni osoba,

223
00:11:26,500 --> 00:11:27,200
 ni plod,

224
00:11:27,200 --> 00:11:29,200
 nego to je bilo to u njihovom žargonu.

225
00:11:31,340 --> 00:11:32,060
 Tako da, eto,

226
00:11:32,060 --> 00:11:34,260
 to nas istavno malo razočaralo,

227
00:11:34,260 --> 00:11:36,080
 jer smo bili u to nekom raskoraku.

228
00:11:36,080 --> 00:11:36,440
 Znači,

229
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:38,700
 znaš kako razmišljaš,

230
00:11:38,700 --> 00:11:41,520
 što ti vjera kaže.

231
00:11:42,680 --> 00:11:45,620
 meni je teško slušati sad dok vi pričate,

232
00:11:45,620 --> 00:11:47,340
 a moli kako je se ona osjećala,

233
00:11:47,340 --> 00:11:51,280
 kad ti tako doktori kažu u paciju.

234
00:11:51,280 --> 00:11:53,220
 Da, jer mi smo bili toliko zbunjeni,

235
00:11:53,220 --> 00:11:54,560
 s jedne strane,

236
00:11:54,560 --> 00:11:54,880
 znači,

237
00:11:54,880 --> 00:11:56,380
 savjesti govori jedno,

238
00:11:56,380 --> 00:11:58,520
 pameti govori jedno,

239
00:11:58,520 --> 00:11:59,920
 struka,

240
00:11:59,920 --> 00:12:00,940
 svi,

241
00:12:00,940 --> 00:12:01,280
 znači,

242
00:12:01,280 --> 00:12:02,240
 svi lježnici,

243
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:03,540
 neće biti dobro,

244
00:12:03,540 --> 00:12:04,420
 to ne valja,

245
00:12:04,420 --> 00:12:05,780
 to se treba riješiti,

246
00:12:06,980 --> 00:12:07,700
 čak ono,

247
00:12:07,700 --> 00:12:09,680
 ste vi svjesni u šta vi ulazite,

248
00:12:09,680 --> 00:12:11,120
 šta to nosi sa sebom,

249
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:13,960
 kao da smo mi bili čudni njima,

250
00:12:13,960 --> 00:12:16,500
 a te kasnije kad sam malo razmišljao,

251
00:12:16,500 --> 00:12:20,040
 sam stvari shvatio da koliko su oni vjerojatno

252
00:12:20,040 --> 00:12:23,500
 se susreću s tim slučajima gdje roditelji

253
00:12:23,500 --> 00:12:27,740
 pokreknu pred tim strafom za tu budućnost svoju,

254
00:12:27,740 --> 00:12:30,180
 možda to napraviti pod izlikom

255
00:12:30,180 --> 00:12:32,000
 budućnosti djeteta,

256
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:33,220
 kakav će on imati život,

257
00:12:33,220 --> 00:12:35,460
 kako će njemu biti,

258
00:12:35,460 --> 00:12:36,900
 u našem slučaju znači njemu,

259
00:12:36,980 --> 00:12:39,940
 a možda sve to pod izlikom

260
00:12:39,940 --> 00:12:42,320
 nekeg svoga komoda,

261
00:12:42,320 --> 00:12:43,860
 svoje sigurnosti u život,

262
00:12:43,860 --> 00:12:47,560
 ne prihvaćanja toga nekoga križa,

263
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:49,660
 neke, da će nam tako,

264
00:12:49,660 --> 00:12:51,820
 najznam križa cijeloživotnog, sigurno.

265
00:12:51,820 --> 00:12:54,200
 Tako da su vjerojatno oni bili,

266
00:12:54,200 --> 00:12:57,620
 više njima uskustva bilo da roditelji

267
00:12:57,620 --> 00:13:00,420
 naprave to što struka savjetuje,

268
00:13:00,420 --> 00:13:02,320
 nego da odbiju,

269
00:13:02,320 --> 00:13:04,920
 tako da su mi njima u stvari bili čudni

270
00:13:04,920 --> 00:13:07,960
 što smo odmah u statu jasno i glasno rekli

271
00:13:07,960 --> 00:13:09,140
 ne, mi nećemo to.

272
00:13:09,560 --> 00:13:11,420
 Koliko su oni vama dali vremena,

273
00:13:11,420 --> 00:13:13,020
 nakon ti svi pregleda na kraj,

274
00:13:13,020 --> 00:13:16,520
 kad se ustanovilo da djeti ima davnom sindrom,

275
00:13:16,520 --> 00:13:18,740
 koliko su vam dali vremena uopće da odlučite,

276
00:13:18,740 --> 00:13:20,320
 da se vas dvoje iskonsultirate,

277
00:13:20,320 --> 00:13:22,400
 da od tim šokom...

278
00:13:22,400 --> 00:13:25,380
 Nije bilo uopće govora o tome vremenu,

279
00:13:25,380 --> 00:13:28,300
 jer znaš stav odmah od početka bio ne i gotovo.

280
00:13:28,300 --> 00:13:32,160
 Da, niko od njih nije nas pitao nikad što vi želite,

281
00:13:32,160 --> 00:13:33,080
 koja je vaša namjera,

282
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:35,260
 nego njima je bilo znači i pretpostavka,

283
00:13:35,260 --> 00:13:36,460
 djete ima sindrom,

284
00:13:36,460 --> 00:13:37,640
 ne valja,

285
00:13:37,640 --> 00:13:38,620
 pod navodnike,

286
00:13:38,620 --> 00:13:40,160
 rješavamo ga se.

287
00:13:40,160 --> 00:13:42,660
 Tako kada smo mi završili,

288
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:45,480
 poslije toga pregleda imali smo još jedan pregled

289
00:13:45,480 --> 00:13:48,800
 kod ljene privatne lješnice u Zagrebu.

290
00:13:48,800 --> 00:13:50,860
 Ona je isto znači potvrdila to,

291
00:13:50,860 --> 00:13:53,380
 savjetovala opet da dobro razmislimo,

292
00:13:53,380 --> 00:13:57,420
 da smo svjesni što mi s time preuzivamo u svojom životu.

293
00:13:57,420 --> 00:14:01,200
 I onda kad smo se vraćali u autobusu iz Splita

294
00:14:01,200 --> 00:14:02,820
 smo dobili poziv.

295
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:04,900
 Iz Zagreba za Splite smo dobili poziv

296
00:14:04,900 --> 00:14:06,620
 da man je bio nalaz gotov,

297
00:14:06,620 --> 00:14:08,160
 to sa Svetog Duha.

298
00:14:08,160 --> 00:14:11,540
 I doktorica mi je rekla kao nalazvan je gotov,

299
00:14:11,540 --> 00:14:13,160
 nije u redu, ja govorim

300
00:14:13,160 --> 00:14:15,120
 šta nije u redu, o čemu se radi,

301
00:14:15,120 --> 00:14:17,620
 kao ima Downov sindrom,

302
00:14:17,620 --> 00:14:19,920
 ja govorim, to vro kao, ok.

303
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:23,540
 I ona meni na to odgovara kao

304
00:14:23,540 --> 00:14:26,640
 ja ću vam poslat kao nalaz mail-on,

305
00:14:26,640 --> 00:14:29,520
 pa vidite u Splitsko rodilište to riješiti.

306
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:33,420
 Ja joj govorim, šta mislite,

307
00:14:33,420 --> 00:14:35,000
 neću ja ništa rješavaka,

308
00:14:35,000 --> 00:14:36,360
 to je naše djete.

309
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:38,700
 I to se ona toliko zvunila,

310
00:14:38,700 --> 00:14:41,260
 toliko je počela zamuckivati,

311
00:14:41,340 --> 00:14:43,040
 nije znala še će mi odgovorit.

312
00:14:43,040 --> 00:14:45,540
 Ono ba, ba, ba, da dobro,

313
00:14:45,540 --> 00:14:46,540
 kao, ok,

314
00:14:46,540 --> 00:14:49,600
 posla će ovo nja mail-on nalaz, pa...

315
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:51,500
 Znači ona je aludirala da odeš u bolunci

316
00:14:51,500 --> 00:14:52,460
 da povaciš, jel da?

317
00:14:52,460 --> 00:14:52,780
 Da.

318
00:14:52,780 --> 00:14:55,040
 Da, znači si cijelo vrijeme

319
00:14:55,040 --> 00:14:56,960
 su doktorji to aludirali i savjetovali,

320
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:59,380
 znači nije uopće bilo razgovor,

321
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:00,220
 da će on mi...

322
00:15:00,220 --> 00:15:00,960
 Povaciš, jel da?

323
00:15:00,960 --> 00:15:01,240
 Da.

324
00:15:01,240 --> 00:15:03,500
 Da, znači si cijelo vrijeme

325
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:06,100
 su doktorji to aludirali i savjetovali,

326
00:15:06,100 --> 00:15:07,860
 znači nije uopće bilo razgovor,

327
00:15:07,860 --> 00:15:09,980
 da će on mi uopće iš drugim smjerom.

328
00:15:09,980 --> 00:15:11,180
 Ovaj...

329
00:15:11,180 --> 00:15:12,100
 O svih tih doktora,

330
00:15:12,100 --> 00:15:13,720
 znači jedino jedan liječnik,

331
00:15:13,720 --> 00:15:15,420
 nakladno kad smo morali napraviti

332
00:15:15,420 --> 00:15:16,660
 ultrazug srca,

333
00:15:16,660 --> 00:15:19,640
 znači i kod fetalnog kardiologa,

334
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:22,040
 koji jedino u Zagrebu na rebru ima,

335
00:15:22,980 --> 00:15:24,020
 i onda kad smo ušli,

336
00:15:24,020 --> 00:15:25,820
 znam, kad sam ušao pogledao sam,

337
00:15:25,820 --> 00:15:26,780
 vidio sam mu na stolu

338
00:15:26,780 --> 00:15:29,760
 glas koncila i sliku majke Tereza,

339
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:31,440
 ja govim, napokon jedan normalan.

340
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:34,140
 I tako je i bilo,

341
00:15:34,140 --> 00:15:35,460
 počeo je pregled,

342
00:15:35,460 --> 00:15:37,160
 jedno 10-15 minuta,

343
00:15:37,160 --> 00:15:38,220
 doktor šuti,

344
00:15:38,220 --> 00:15:38,900
 gleda,

345
00:15:38,900 --> 00:15:40,300
 ja njemu iza leđa,

346
00:15:40,300 --> 00:15:40,740
 gledam nju,

347
00:15:40,740 --> 00:15:42,600
 ona mene zbunja,

348
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:43,620
 ni šta će sad bit?

349
00:15:43,620 --> 00:15:45,420
 Ja on progovorim,

350
00:15:45,420 --> 00:15:46,460
 dobro je sve u redu,

351
00:15:47,180 --> 00:15:49,180
 u čemu je kvaka,

352
00:15:49,180 --> 00:15:54,560
 oko 60% djece sa daunom sindromom

353
00:15:54,560 --> 00:15:57,820
 se rodi sa srčanom manom,

354
00:15:57,820 --> 00:15:59,740
 što manjom, što većom,

355
00:15:59,740 --> 00:16:03,700
 većinom je potreban operativni zahvat

356
00:16:03,700 --> 00:16:04,760
 odmah po rođenju,

357
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:05,680
 i to ne jedan,

358
00:16:05,680 --> 00:16:06,640
 obično bude više,

359
00:16:06,640 --> 00:16:10,720
 automatski činje srce u razvoju,

360
00:16:10,720 --> 00:16:11,380
 nije u redu,

361
00:16:11,380 --> 00:16:13,300
 cijeli organizam se loše razvije.

362
00:16:13,300 --> 00:16:15,640
 Dok je namo sad i ta lješnik,

363
00:16:15,640 --> 00:16:16,940
 ono s čudom gledao,

364
00:16:17,180 --> 00:16:18,080
 gleda nalaz,

365
00:16:18,080 --> 00:16:20,180
 znači potvrđeno da je daunov sindrom,

366
00:16:20,180 --> 00:16:22,480
 znam samo da je rekao da je srce

367
00:16:22,480 --> 00:16:25,380
 dobro ne za djete s daunovim sindromom,

368
00:16:25,380 --> 00:16:28,280
 nego čak i za djete bez poteškoća,

369
00:16:28,280 --> 00:16:29,240
 ono,

370
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:30,780
 zdravo srce,

371
00:16:30,780 --> 00:16:32,120
 100%.

372
00:16:32,120 --> 00:16:37,360
 Kako si se ti tada osjećao?

373
00:16:37,360 --> 00:16:39,300
 Kako si proživljava to sve?

374
00:16:39,300 --> 00:16:41,120
 Pa olakšanje,

375
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:42,480
 prvo što napoko ima neko

376
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:45,500
 s nekim normalnim razgovarat,

377
00:16:45,500 --> 00:16:47,400
 jer nakon pregleda on nama rekao,

378
00:16:47,400 --> 00:16:49,580
 a mora reći da se ne bojimo,

379
00:16:49,580 --> 00:16:53,400
 da se s djecom s daunovim sindromom može puno toga postići,

380
00:16:53,400 --> 00:16:56,000
 da se treba raditi puno,

381
00:16:56,000 --> 00:17:01,260
 ali da se to nosi normalno svoju ljepotu i radost.

382
00:17:01,500 --> 00:17:04,080
 Na kraju, vamu reći ono,

383
00:17:04,080 --> 00:17:06,080
 bilo mu je drago da smo,

384
00:17:06,080 --> 00:17:09,000
 to nam je rekao da mu je drago da smo se odlučili išći do kraja,

385
00:17:09,000 --> 00:17:11,120
 da nismo prekinuli trudnoć.

386
00:17:11,120 --> 00:17:14,560
 A jeste li u tom periodu,

387
00:17:14,560 --> 00:17:16,100
 mislim rodbina naravno,

388
00:17:16,100 --> 00:17:16,900
 prijatelji si,

389
00:17:16,900 --> 00:17:19,760
 jer vidim da i ovdje neki prijatelji pozdravljaju kumove i tako,

390
00:17:20,340 --> 00:17:22,180
 kako je okolina reagirala,

391
00:17:22,180 --> 00:17:23,580
 jer su znali što se događa,

392
00:17:23,580 --> 00:17:27,500
 jer najčešće nekada je i okolina veliki pritisak.

393
00:17:29,300 --> 00:17:32,620
 Naši stvarno su i roditelji i braća i sestre,

394
00:17:32,620 --> 00:17:35,740
 stvarno najbliža rodbina je bila uz nas od prvoga dana.

395
00:17:35,740 --> 00:17:41,960
 Podupirali su na šta god da smo mi odlučili,

396
00:17:41,960 --> 00:17:45,960
 stali su iza nas doslovce,

397
00:17:45,960 --> 00:17:51,400
 dok ono malo dalji su govorili kao pre mladi ste,

398
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:54,080
 šta vama to treba i tako dalje,

399
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:56,280
 ali njih nismo slušali.

400
00:17:58,180 --> 00:18:01,140
 A ko vam je onda bio najveća podrška u tom periodu?

401
00:18:01,140 --> 00:18:04,540
 Pa mislim, baš naša je to obitelj,

402
00:18:04,540 --> 00:18:07,180
 i njezina i moja strana,

403
00:18:07,180 --> 00:18:08,320
 stvarno su veke,

404
00:18:08,320 --> 00:18:10,420
 kad je to još bilo na početku,

405
00:18:10,420 --> 00:18:11,220
 što god odlučite,

406
00:18:11,220 --> 00:18:12,220
 mi smo uz vas,

407
00:18:12,220 --> 00:18:16,040
 znači i u molitvi i u svemu,

408
00:18:16,040 --> 00:18:18,680
 jer, znači želim,

409
00:18:18,680 --> 00:18:20,340
 krenuti s ovom temom,

410
00:18:20,340 --> 00:18:22,000
 znači malo vjerskom,

411
00:18:22,000 --> 00:18:25,800
 molitva je ovdje učinila jedno veliko čudo.

412
00:18:27,060 --> 00:18:29,100
 Znači, da je neko vidio,

413
00:18:29,100 --> 00:18:29,900
 pogotovo ko se,

414
00:18:29,900 --> 00:18:31,580
 da je to razumiju malo više u to,

415
00:18:31,580 --> 00:18:38,280
 nalaz, to jest snimku ultrazvuka,

416
00:18:38,280 --> 00:18:39,760
 znači naš Dominik,

417
00:18:39,760 --> 00:18:43,020
 kad je bio veličina otprilike 6 centimetara,

418
00:18:43,020 --> 00:18:45,360
 kad je bio kao djete,

419
00:18:45,360 --> 00:18:46,080
 kao plod,

420
00:18:46,080 --> 00:18:48,980
 znači on je bio imao taj nabor

421
00:18:48,980 --> 00:18:50,020
 i obavijen to tekućinom,

422
00:18:51,100 --> 00:18:53,160
 koji oni nisu uopće znali što je to,

423
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:54,020
 oni nisu uspili nama,

424
00:18:54,020 --> 00:18:57,840
 to što mi nismo dobili na kraju potvrdu šta je to bilo.

425
00:18:57,840 --> 00:19:03,220
 To je bilo 8 milimetara debljine od glave leđa,

426
00:19:03,220 --> 00:19:06,260
 jedino, mislim, lice i trbuh nije bilo obavijeno.

427
00:19:06,260 --> 00:19:09,500
 i glice, mislim, samo nije bilo.

428
00:19:09,500 --> 00:19:14,240
 I to je stvarno bilo bružno za vidjeti u tom omjeru tada,

429
00:19:14,240 --> 00:19:15,280
 znači kada smo imali.

430
00:19:15,280 --> 00:19:18,940
 I normalno priča se raširila,

431
00:19:18,940 --> 00:19:23,680
 znači unutar naše obitelji, rodbine, prijatelja,

432
00:19:23,680 --> 00:19:27,100
 i ta molitva je krenula,

433
00:19:27,100 --> 00:19:29,040
 širila se sve više,

434
00:19:29,040 --> 00:19:35,600
 i jednostavno čudo se počelo događati.

435
00:19:35,600 --> 00:19:40,180
 Znači, prvo, Betoviš želi napomenuti jednu stvar,

436
00:19:40,180 --> 00:19:42,920
 znači u ovim tako teškim trenucima,

437
00:19:42,920 --> 00:19:48,760
 teško je pokazati da će tako vjeru,

438
00:19:48,760 --> 00:19:51,740
 onu konkretnu, lako je govoriti,

439
00:19:51,740 --> 00:19:53,080
 gospodine, ja vjerujem,

440
00:19:53,080 --> 00:19:56,380
 ali kad zagusti, e onda krene,

441
00:19:56,380 --> 00:19:58,020
 jer mi kad smo saznali ovo,

442
00:19:58,020 --> 00:20:00,520
 to je bilo pri par dana,

443
00:20:00,520 --> 00:20:04,320
 emocije divljaju od plakanja,

444
00:20:04,940 --> 00:20:09,460
 suza suza ugorni, ti više ne znaš kako razmišljati,

445
00:20:09,460 --> 00:20:10,300
 pa Bože, zašto?

446
00:20:10,300 --> 00:20:12,520
 Pa, stvarno ti misliš da to mogu,

447
00:20:12,580 --> 00:20:14,580
 mislim, zašto mi, ono,

448
00:20:14,580 --> 00:20:17,660
 ono, djelostavno ne možeš to pojmiti,

449
00:20:17,660 --> 00:20:21,680
 i bio je tada, znači, ono Božečno,

450
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:23,280
 prvo Božečno vrijeme, advent,

451
00:20:23,280 --> 00:20:25,340
 i znam da sam otišao ovdje,

452
00:20:25,340 --> 00:20:26,660
 pošto živimo u Solinu,

453
00:20:26,660 --> 00:20:28,100
 radimo u Splitu, živimo u Solinu,

454
00:20:28,100 --> 00:20:30,820
 u crku Odeh,

455
00:20:30,820 --> 00:20:32,100
 i ovdje sam otišao na Misu Zornicu,

456
00:20:32,100 --> 00:20:35,560
 ali, eto, iz nekog razloga,

457
00:20:35,560 --> 00:20:37,520
 možda i to bila providnost,

458
00:20:37,520 --> 00:20:38,800
 u puno slučajeva,

459
00:20:38,800 --> 00:20:40,380
 evo, kaj je ovaj naš susret,

460
00:20:40,380 --> 00:20:41,000
 oprije mjesec,

461
00:20:41,000 --> 00:20:42,580
 danas se nismo uopće ni znali,

462
00:20:42,580 --> 00:20:43,900
 ni poznavali,

463
00:20:43,900 --> 00:20:45,440
 evo, već smo odeo u live-u s vama,

464
00:20:46,520 --> 00:20:48,040
 otišao sam na tu zornicu,

465
00:20:48,040 --> 00:20:48,580
 to je zornic,

466
00:20:48,580 --> 00:20:49,280
 već bila gotova,

467
00:20:49,280 --> 00:20:51,240
 ja sam pogriješao kaj je termin,

468
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:53,020
 i sa u Solinu ima,

469
00:20:53,020 --> 00:20:54,580
 znači, nakon ulaznih vrata,

470
00:20:54,580 --> 00:20:55,740
 par metara prostora,

471
00:20:55,740 --> 00:20:57,040
 nas je jedna stakljena vrata,

472
00:20:57,040 --> 00:21:00,200
 nije bilo nikoga tada,

473
00:21:00,200 --> 00:21:02,140
 bilo možda šesti po sedam ujutro,

474
00:21:02,140 --> 00:21:03,860
 znam da sam tu kleknio,

475
00:21:03,860 --> 00:21:04,760
 i prvi put,

476
00:21:04,760 --> 00:21:06,100
 stvarno ono iskreno,

477
00:21:06,100 --> 00:21:07,800
 Bogu iznio sve,

478
00:21:07,800 --> 00:21:09,940
 kod da pričam s nabojim prijateljem,

479
00:21:09,940 --> 00:21:10,680
 sa bratom,

480
00:21:10,680 --> 00:21:13,520
 i jednostavno ja sam reklamo,

481
00:21:13,520 --> 00:21:13,920
 Bože,

482
00:21:13,920 --> 00:21:15,020
 ja vjerujem,

483
00:21:15,440 --> 00:21:17,320
 uvijek sve vjerujem da je s nekim razlogom,

484
00:21:17,320 --> 00:21:19,040
 znači, ne studbina,

485
00:21:19,040 --> 00:21:19,800
 nego kao ste vi rekli,

486
00:21:19,800 --> 00:21:20,500
 prst Boži,

487
00:21:20,500 --> 00:21:23,660
 znači, da je sve s nekim razlogom,

488
00:21:23,660 --> 00:21:24,480
 ja sam rekao,

489
00:21:24,480 --> 00:21:25,080
 Bože, dobro,

490
00:21:25,080 --> 00:21:26,220
 ti imaš neki plan,

491
00:21:26,220 --> 00:21:27,640
 ali ja,

492
00:21:27,640 --> 00:21:28,680
 Sanja,

493
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:29,500
 mi to ne možemo,

494
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:29,820
 znači,

495
00:21:29,820 --> 00:21:31,680
 mi sa svojim naporom,

496
00:21:31,680 --> 00:21:32,300
 svojom snagom,

497
00:21:32,300 --> 00:21:33,380
 mi to ne možemo napraviti,

498
00:21:33,380 --> 00:21:33,680
 znači,

499
00:21:33,680 --> 00:21:35,020
 trebaš nam ti,

500
00:21:35,020 --> 00:21:36,300
 tvoja pomoć,

501
00:21:36,300 --> 00:21:37,500
 tvoje vosto,

502
00:21:37,500 --> 00:21:38,120
 ti gospodine,

503
00:21:38,120 --> 00:21:39,060
 preuzmi ti vodi,

504
00:21:39,060 --> 00:21:42,360
 i tu sam prvo neko vrijeme,

505
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:43,220
 znači,

506
00:21:43,220 --> 00:21:44,460
 sve što mi je bilo na duši,

507
00:21:44,460 --> 00:21:46,680
 na srcu sam rekao gospodinu

508
00:21:46,680 --> 00:21:48,280
 i već,

509
00:21:48,280 --> 00:21:48,660
 znači,

510
00:21:48,660 --> 00:21:49,340
 neki mir,

511
00:21:49,340 --> 00:21:50,320
 osjetio da će,

512
00:21:50,320 --> 00:21:51,740
 da će bit,

513
00:21:51,740 --> 00:21:53,120
 bit sve u redu,

514
00:21:53,120 --> 00:21:55,280
 a zašto,

515
00:21:55,280 --> 00:21:55,820
 imamo reć,

516
00:21:55,820 --> 00:21:58,020
 oprosti što se ubacujem,

517
00:21:58,020 --> 00:21:59,720
 a mislim da takih situacija,

518
00:21:59,720 --> 00:22:01,180
 nekako teže muškarcima,

519
00:22:01,180 --> 00:22:02,120
 slomice,

520
00:22:02,120 --> 00:22:04,740
 majke dobio odmah taj maječinski,

521
00:22:04,740 --> 00:22:05,520
 neki osjećaj,

522
00:22:05,520 --> 00:22:06,700
 instikt maječinstva,

523
00:22:06,700 --> 00:22:08,220
 i one puno ne kalkuliraju,

524
00:22:08,220 --> 00:22:09,780
 ali mislim da je nekako muškarcima,

525
00:22:09,780 --> 00:22:11,600
 ono što sad pričaš,

526
00:22:11,600 --> 00:22:12,400
 da si proživljava,

527
00:22:12,480 --> 00:22:23,720
 jer na početku je bilo straha za budućnost,

528
00:22:23,720 --> 00:22:24,820
 znači što, kako,

529
00:22:24,820 --> 00:22:27,380
 toliko od toga ti prođe kroz glavu,

530
00:22:27,380 --> 00:22:28,860
 šta će bit s tim djetetom,

531
00:22:28,860 --> 00:22:30,940
 odmah kakvi će život imati,

532
00:22:30,940 --> 00:22:32,920
 šta kad nas ne bude jednog dana,

533
00:22:32,920 --> 00:22:35,220
 o čemu li li će imati više djece iza njega,

534
00:22:35,220 --> 00:22:38,120
 toliko tih pitanja je bilo,

535
00:22:38,120 --> 00:22:39,500
 ali,

536
00:22:39,500 --> 00:22:41,620
 evo, volio bi istaknuti,

537
00:22:41,620 --> 00:22:44,560
 kao ste vi isto sa drugim gostima znali,

538
00:22:44,560 --> 00:22:46,580
 ono, neko štivo preporučiti,

539
00:22:46,580 --> 00:22:49,340
 znači knjiga koja je meni promijenila život,

540
00:22:49,340 --> 00:22:51,040
 znači to je

541
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:53,460
 dnevnik Svete Faustine Kovalske,

542
00:22:53,460 --> 00:22:55,680
 eto preporučan,

543
00:22:55,680 --> 00:22:57,740
 ako ko ima priliku je nabaviti,

544
00:22:57,740 --> 00:22:58,760
 možda čak u ovom periodu,

545
00:22:58,760 --> 00:23:00,160
 kad smo svi doma imate vremena,

546
00:23:00,160 --> 00:23:01,400
 je da malo ima više stranica,

547
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:02,680
 skoro 500 stranica,

548
00:23:02,680 --> 00:23:04,760
 gdje, znači,

549
00:23:04,760 --> 00:23:06,160
 Isus Svete Faustini

550
00:23:06,160 --> 00:23:07,680
 pokazuje,

551
00:23:07,680 --> 00:23:10,080
 znači, smisao patnje,

552
00:23:10,760 --> 00:23:13,440
 smisao poteškoće u životu

553
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:16,760
 i želim naglasiti,

554
00:23:16,760 --> 00:23:18,740
 kao što se i vi u jednoj emisiji,

555
00:23:18,740 --> 00:23:19,220
 znači,

556
00:23:19,220 --> 00:23:20,680
 Bog ne kažnjava,

557
00:23:20,680 --> 00:23:23,720
 Bog preko patnje,

558
00:23:23,720 --> 00:23:26,120
 preko nekog križa,

559
00:23:26,120 --> 00:23:27,420
 jedino spašava,

560
00:23:27,420 --> 00:23:28,400
 ili nas,

561
00:23:28,400 --> 00:23:29,660
 ili nekoga drugoga.

562
00:23:29,660 --> 00:23:31,780
 Sveta Faustina je umrla,

563
00:23:31,780 --> 00:23:33,760
 mlada u 33. godini,

564
00:23:33,760 --> 00:23:34,540
 sa toliko,

565
00:23:35,400 --> 00:23:37,840
 bolesti na svom tijelu,

566
00:23:37,840 --> 00:23:38,480
 koja je sve

567
00:23:38,480 --> 00:23:41,820
 prihvatila svojevoljno

568
00:23:41,820 --> 00:23:43,760
 za spas drugih,

569
00:23:43,760 --> 00:23:45,420
 pogotovo duša u čistilištu.

570
00:23:45,420 --> 00:23:47,160
 I tada sam,

571
00:23:47,160 --> 00:23:48,740
 od kad sam pročitao ovu knjigu,

572
00:23:48,740 --> 00:23:49,260
 ja sam

573
00:23:49,260 --> 00:23:50,080
 počeo

574
00:23:50,080 --> 00:23:52,080
 i prihvatio da u svom životu

575
00:23:52,080 --> 00:23:52,980
 da je znači sve,

576
00:23:52,980 --> 00:23:53,780
 apsolutno sve

577
00:23:53,780 --> 00:23:54,840
 s nekim razlogom,

578
00:23:54,840 --> 00:23:56,220
 bit će biljivo,

579
00:23:56,220 --> 00:23:57,760
 ili Lizu,

580
00:23:57,760 --> 00:23:58,720
 ili jednoga dana,

581
00:23:58,720 --> 00:23:59,580
 uvijek ćeš shvatiti

582
00:23:59,580 --> 00:24:00,700
 kad imaš neki križ,

583
00:24:00,700 --> 00:24:02,120
 zašto je to bilo,

584
00:24:02,120 --> 00:24:03,540
 zašto te godi možda pripremao,

585
00:24:03,540 --> 00:24:04,880
 za možda još nešto veće,

586
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:07,080
 tu ljepotu ćeš vidjeti,

587
00:24:07,080 --> 00:24:09,440
 kad tad srpljenja treba imati.

588
00:24:09,440 --> 00:24:11,040
 I znao sam,

589
00:24:11,040 --> 00:24:11,580
 znači,

590
00:24:11,580 --> 00:24:13,160
 da Bog ima neki plan.

591
00:24:13,160 --> 00:24:14,960
 Samo treba onda

592
00:24:14,960 --> 00:24:16,580
 znati živjeti,

593
00:24:16,580 --> 00:24:18,420
 ono što svaki dan molimo,

594
00:24:18,420 --> 00:24:19,700
 budi volja tvoja,

595
00:24:20,220 --> 00:24:22,180
 da ne bude samo puko izgovaranje,

596
00:24:22,180 --> 00:24:24,660
 nego da mi stvarno u srcu to

597
00:24:24,660 --> 00:24:28,240
 priznamo i da znamo,

598
00:24:28,240 --> 00:24:29,300
 gospodine,

599
00:24:29,300 --> 00:24:30,540
 evo sad je neki problem,

600
00:24:30,540 --> 00:24:33,640
 ali ti znaš zašto ti si to planirao,

601
00:24:33,640 --> 00:24:34,520
 ti vodi

602
00:24:34,520 --> 00:24:36,420
 i neka se ispuni tvoja volja.

603
00:24:36,420 --> 00:24:37,380
 To je, znači,

604
00:24:37,380 --> 00:24:38,420
 mene promijenilo

605
00:24:38,420 --> 00:24:40,640
 i da nije bilo toga,

606
00:24:40,640 --> 00:24:41,920
 sigurno bi teško

607
00:24:41,920 --> 00:24:43,800
 i ko zna kako prihvati ovaj križ,

608
00:24:43,800 --> 00:24:45,340
 ali, znači,

609
00:24:45,340 --> 00:24:47,680
 providnost Božja je bila da,

610
00:24:47,680 --> 00:24:49,940
 da Bogu hvala,

611
00:24:50,220 --> 00:24:51,820
 promijeni svoje mišljenje,

612
00:24:51,820 --> 00:24:52,620
 dovolja.

613
00:24:52,620 --> 00:24:54,480
 Sad nije jasno

614
00:24:54,480 --> 00:24:56,300
 zašto smo se ja ti brzo povezali

615
00:24:56,300 --> 00:24:58,320
 sa vama,

616
00:24:58,320 --> 00:24:59,700
 jer vidiš Milosavnog tu,

617
00:24:59,700 --> 00:25:00,560
 znači,

618
00:25:00,560 --> 00:25:01,860
 on i Paustina,

619
00:25:01,860 --> 00:25:03,180
 očigledno imaju prste

620
00:25:03,180 --> 00:25:04,200
 i kod mene i kod vas.

621
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:06,760
 Drago me da si jel

622
00:25:06,760 --> 00:25:08,560
 istaknu Dnevnih sestre Paustine,

623
00:25:08,560 --> 00:25:09,240
 neki da opite

624
00:25:09,240 --> 00:25:09,960
 koja je to knjiga,

625
00:25:09,960 --> 00:25:11,660
 zove se Dnevnih sestre Paustine

626
00:25:11,660 --> 00:25:12,840
 i slobodno je,

627
00:25:12,840 --> 00:25:13,580
 čitajte ljudi,

628
00:25:13,580 --> 00:25:15,400
 nemojte čitati u komadu,

629
00:25:15,760 --> 00:25:16,200
 dovoljno,

630
00:25:16,200 --> 00:25:17,160
 jedna stranica,

631
00:25:17,160 --> 00:25:18,200
 imate što razmišljati.

632
00:25:18,200 --> 00:25:21,260
 Želiš ti nešto reći,

633
00:25:21,260 --> 00:25:23,140
 mama?

634
00:25:23,140 --> 00:25:24,640
 I ovaj,

635
00:25:24,640 --> 00:25:25,360
 znači,

636
00:25:25,360 --> 00:25:26,100
 naš put,

637
00:25:26,100 --> 00:25:26,340
 evo,

638
00:25:26,340 --> 00:25:28,500
 za odlazak,

639
00:25:28,500 --> 00:25:28,880
 znači,

640
00:25:28,880 --> 00:25:30,580
 nakon,

641
00:25:30,580 --> 00:25:31,240
 znači,

642
00:25:31,240 --> 00:25:32,500
 išao je taj neki period

643
00:25:32,500 --> 00:25:34,500
 prihvaćanja toga,

644
00:25:34,500 --> 00:25:35,900
 to je kad smo se mi pomirili

645
00:25:35,900 --> 00:25:36,560
 sa svim,

646
00:25:36,560 --> 00:25:38,440
 i zatim smo otišli,

647
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:38,700
 znači,

648
00:25:38,700 --> 00:25:39,140
 opet,

649
00:25:39,140 --> 00:25:40,800
 ja volim to reći,

650
00:25:40,860 --> 00:25:41,800
 providnost Božja,

651
00:25:41,800 --> 00:25:44,580
 naš prijatelj,

652
00:25:44,580 --> 00:25:45,660
 Nikola Šakić,

653
00:25:45,660 --> 00:25:46,040
 koji je,

654
00:25:46,040 --> 00:25:46,200
 evo,

655
00:25:46,200 --> 00:25:46,980
 vogu hvala,

656
00:25:46,980 --> 00:25:48,300
 još za koji mjeseć,

657
00:25:48,300 --> 00:25:49,620
 je mladomisnik,

658
00:25:49,620 --> 00:25:51,580
 bivši kolega,

659
00:25:51,580 --> 00:25:51,880
 znači,

660
00:25:51,880 --> 00:25:53,320
 bili smo zajedno na istom brodu

661
00:25:53,320 --> 00:25:54,140
 u Mornarici,

662
00:25:54,140 --> 00:25:55,360
 gdje radim,

663
00:25:55,360 --> 00:25:57,200
 ovaj,

664
00:25:57,200 --> 00:25:57,980
 on je,

665
00:25:57,980 --> 00:25:58,840
 kad sam ja počeo

666
00:25:58,840 --> 00:25:59,980
 radit dvih desete,

667
00:25:59,980 --> 00:26:02,120
 na tom brodu,

668
00:26:02,120 --> 00:26:03,700
 on je tada još bio vojnik,

669
00:26:03,700 --> 00:26:04,600
 topnik,

670
00:26:04,600 --> 00:26:06,060
 pa se volimo zezati,

671
00:26:06,060 --> 00:26:07,020
 da je njegov put bio

672
00:26:07,020 --> 00:26:08,360
 od topa do popa,

673
00:26:09,140 --> 00:26:11,760
 i evo još za koji mjeseć će biti svečenik,

674
00:26:11,760 --> 00:26:13,180
 i on je,

675
00:26:13,180 --> 00:26:13,520
 znači,

676
00:26:13,520 --> 00:26:14,980
 bila je duhovna obnova

677
00:26:14,980 --> 00:26:17,040
 u župi Katuni,

678
00:26:17,040 --> 00:26:17,660
 Kreševo,

679
00:26:17,660 --> 00:26:19,920
 to je kod Don Mija Grozdanića,

680
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:22,600
 za njega ste čuli ovih dana po medijima,

681
00:26:22,600 --> 00:26:25,540
 kad je bio sa presvetim po selu,

682
00:26:25,540 --> 00:26:26,460
 išao i danas,

683
00:26:26,460 --> 00:26:28,640
 kako je svim župljanima dostavio,

684
00:26:28,640 --> 00:26:29,180
 znači,

685
00:26:29,180 --> 00:26:30,900
 palmine, grančice,

686
00:26:30,900 --> 00:26:31,440
 križ,

687
00:26:31,440 --> 00:26:31,800
 vodu,

688
00:26:31,800 --> 00:26:33,360
 sol i sve što treba,

689
00:26:33,360 --> 00:26:35,640
 i, znači,

690
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:37,020
 opet mi smo dobili poziv,

691
00:26:37,020 --> 00:26:38,300
 kao poziv u Međugorje,

692
00:26:38,380 --> 00:26:41,080
 tako i poziv za tu duhovnu obnovu,

693
00:26:41,080 --> 00:26:41,940
 trodnevnicu,

694
00:26:41,940 --> 00:26:43,360
 opet preko nekoga,

695
00:26:43,360 --> 00:26:43,760
 znači,

696
00:26:43,760 --> 00:26:47,600
 Bog je to sve planirao i za nas,

697
00:26:49,600 --> 00:26:51,240
 i, znači,

698
00:26:51,240 --> 00:26:52,440
 šti moleć,

699
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:52,920
 ja sve,

700
00:26:52,920 --> 00:26:55,360
 i bili smo,

701
00:26:55,360 --> 00:26:55,580
 znači,

702
00:26:55,580 --> 00:26:56,640
 na to duhovno obnovi,

703
00:26:56,640 --> 00:26:57,620
 na kraju,

704
00:26:57,620 --> 00:26:59,300
 je bilo,

705
00:26:59,300 --> 00:27:00,900
 polaganje ruku,

706
00:27:00,900 --> 00:27:02,640
 i tada je,

707
00:27:02,640 --> 00:27:02,980
 znači,

708
00:27:02,980 --> 00:27:03,740
 u tom trenu,

709
00:27:03,740 --> 00:27:04,960
 kad je svećenik,

710
00:27:05,500 --> 00:27:07,820
 položio ruke na nas,

711
00:27:07,820 --> 00:27:10,120
 mi smo se držali za ruke,

712
00:27:10,120 --> 00:27:12,520
 ja sam zatvorio oči i osjetio,

713
00:27:12,520 --> 00:27:12,880
 znači,

714
00:27:12,880 --> 00:27:15,600
 da me duh sveti preuzima,

715
00:27:15,600 --> 00:27:17,420
 i mi na kraju,

716
00:27:17,420 --> 00:27:17,780
 kad sam,

717
00:27:17,780 --> 00:27:18,360
 znači,

718
00:27:18,360 --> 00:27:20,180
 na podu otvorio oči,

719
00:27:20,180 --> 00:27:20,580
 vidim,

720
00:27:20,580 --> 00:27:21,980
 leži ona kraj mene,

721
00:27:21,980 --> 00:27:23,340
 i dalje se držimo za ruke,

722
00:27:23,340 --> 00:27:24,940
 nas su nam ljudi rekli,

723
00:27:24,940 --> 00:27:25,860
 da smo mi isto vremeno,

724
00:27:25,860 --> 00:27:27,620
 pođivali u duhu,

725
00:27:27,620 --> 00:27:30,400
 i kad smo se ustali,

726
00:27:30,400 --> 00:27:31,700
 svećenik nas je zagrljio,

727
00:27:31,700 --> 00:27:32,680
 blagoslovio,

728
00:27:32,680 --> 00:27:34,840
 i nevjerojatno,

729
00:27:34,840 --> 00:27:36,860
 kakav smo mi mir osjetili,

730
00:27:36,860 --> 00:27:38,160
 znači,

731
00:27:38,160 --> 00:27:40,780
 ušli smo kao jedne osobe u tu crkvu,

732
00:27:40,780 --> 00:27:43,420
 izašli kao totalno promijenjene,

733
00:27:43,420 --> 00:27:45,760
 ispunjeni tolikim mirom,

734
00:27:45,760 --> 00:27:47,880
 da će sve biti u redu,

735
00:27:47,880 --> 00:27:50,400
 da je to jednostavno,

736
00:27:50,400 --> 00:27:51,960
 bi bilo neopisivo,

737
00:27:51,960 --> 00:27:54,480
 i nakon toga,

738
00:27:54,480 --> 00:27:54,780
 znači,

739
00:27:54,780 --> 00:27:55,800
 bi opet pregled,

740
00:27:55,800 --> 00:27:57,360
 nakon toga je bio pregled,

741
00:27:57,440 --> 00:27:58,480
 i ona sva tekućina,

742
00:27:58,480 --> 00:27:59,880
 koja je bila oko Dominika,

743
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:00,980
 se povukla.

744
00:28:00,980 --> 00:28:04,500
 Znači, jednostavno je sve nestalo.

745
00:28:04,500 --> 00:28:05,600
 A opet,

746
00:28:05,600 --> 00:28:07,820
 dašto šelim puno toga naglasiti,

747
00:28:07,820 --> 00:28:10,400
 jer puno roditelja,

748
00:28:10,400 --> 00:28:13,400
 da li će tako ne imalo milost,

749
00:28:13,400 --> 00:28:15,060
 možda nekad i bolje,

750
00:28:15,060 --> 00:28:16,600
 ne znam kako bi reagirali,

751
00:28:16,600 --> 00:28:20,760
 ali puno roditelja sazna za djecu,

752
00:28:20,760 --> 00:28:22,060
 znači po porodu,

753
00:28:22,060 --> 00:28:23,700
 da imaju Downo sindrom.

754
00:28:23,700 --> 00:28:26,480
 I onda tu bude veliko razočaranje.

755
00:28:26,480 --> 00:28:27,240
 Šok.

756
00:28:27,260 --> 00:28:28,360
 šok i sve.

757
00:28:28,360 --> 00:28:29,880
 Mi smo imali,

758
00:28:29,880 --> 00:28:30,160
 znači,

759
00:28:30,160 --> 00:28:32,240
 tu sreću da smo uvidjeli

760
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,400
 da nešto nije u redu.

761
00:28:33,400 --> 00:28:35,760
 Imali smo vremena pripremi se,

762
00:28:35,760 --> 00:28:37,640
 jedno s drugim,

763
00:28:37,640 --> 00:28:38,760
 sa gospodinom.

764
00:28:38,760 --> 00:28:41,240
 I onda je Bog napravio to čudo,

765
00:28:41,240 --> 00:28:41,580
 gdje je,

766
00:28:41,580 --> 00:28:42,020
 znači,

767
00:28:42,020 --> 00:28:45,160
 po rukama svećenika,

768
00:28:45,160 --> 00:28:46,600
 udjelio nama mir,

769
00:28:47,760 --> 00:28:49,140
 i mi vjerujemo,

770
00:28:49,140 --> 00:28:51,640
 uklonio sve to što je bilo,

771
00:28:51,640 --> 00:28:53,560
 ugrožavalo njegov život.

772
00:28:53,560 --> 00:28:55,680
 Znali smo,

773
00:28:55,680 --> 00:28:56,040
 znači,

774
00:28:56,040 --> 00:28:57,780
 iskreno nismo vjerali da će

775
00:28:57,780 --> 00:29:00,480
 sindrom kao sindrom cijeli nestati,

776
00:29:00,480 --> 00:29:02,080
 ali s obzirom,

777
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:02,440
 znači,

778
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:03,800
 sad smo više u toj temi,

779
00:29:03,800 --> 00:29:05,620
 koliko ljudi,

780
00:29:05,660 --> 00:29:05,920
 znači,

781
00:29:05,920 --> 00:29:07,960
 ima djecu sa velikim,

782
00:29:07,960 --> 00:29:09,240
 zdravstvenim po teškovačama,

783
00:29:09,240 --> 00:29:11,220
 govorimo o djeci sa Down-ovim sindromom.

784
00:29:11,220 --> 00:29:12,660
 Znači,

785
00:29:12,660 --> 00:29:15,140
 naš Dominik nema ni srčanu grešku,

786
00:29:15,140 --> 00:29:16,620
 nikakvu drugu popratnu,

787
00:29:16,620 --> 00:29:17,860
 rečano maliju,

788
00:29:17,860 --> 00:29:19,440
 neko zdravstveno stanje,

789
00:29:19,440 --> 00:29:22,340
 koje ga teže,

790
00:29:22,340 --> 00:29:23,980
 koje ga kođi tu život.

791
00:29:23,980 --> 00:29:26,480
 I smatram da je to isto veliko čudo,

792
00:29:26,480 --> 00:29:29,620
 znamenje i blagoslov koji smo dobili,

793
00:29:29,620 --> 00:29:30,320
 kada smo svano

794
00:29:30,320 --> 00:29:32,220
 gospodinu rekli da,

795
00:29:32,220 --> 00:29:34,620
 i prihvatili to što nam je dao.

796
00:29:35,020 --> 00:29:35,860
 Jer je bitno,

797
00:29:35,860 --> 00:29:38,880
 bitno gospodinu dati prostora da on djeluje.

798
00:29:38,880 --> 00:29:40,340
 Ako smo mi zatvoreni,

799
00:29:40,340 --> 00:29:42,340
 on nama daje tu slobodu.

800
00:29:42,340 --> 00:29:44,120
 Češ ti ići ljevo, desno,

801
00:29:44,120 --> 00:29:45,380
 radi što ga hoćeš.

802
00:29:45,380 --> 00:29:49,260
 Ali opet kada mi se uvidimo gdje smo,

803
00:29:49,260 --> 00:29:50,380
 kada damo tu ruku,

804
00:29:50,380 --> 00:29:52,940
 stvarno čuda se događaju,

805
00:29:52,940 --> 00:29:54,640
 na slavu njegovu,

806
00:29:54,640 --> 00:29:58,540
 a i da drugi vide i znamo zašto.

807
00:29:58,540 --> 00:30:03,220
 Samo ni nastavite pričati,

808
00:30:03,320 --> 00:30:05,700
 meni je doliko teško i pitanja vam uopće postavljati.

809
00:30:05,700 --> 00:30:06,260
 Da.

810
00:30:06,260 --> 00:30:11,540
 Uvidjela sam odaj jedno pitanje u vezi poroda.

811
00:30:11,540 --> 00:30:14,840
 Porod kao porod je bio odličan,

812
00:30:14,840 --> 00:30:16,580
 osoblje super.

813
00:30:17,980 --> 00:30:20,560
 čak čin se rodio Dominik,

814
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:24,420
 počeo je mijenjati ljude oko sebe.

815
00:30:24,420 --> 00:30:27,200
 Jer oni kad su vidjeli,

816
00:30:27,200 --> 00:30:28,940
 kako smo mi njega zagrljeli,

817
00:30:28,940 --> 00:30:31,020
 kako smo mi njega počeli ljubiti,

818
00:30:31,020 --> 00:30:33,540
 sriću u našim očima,

819
00:30:33,540 --> 00:30:36,800
 jednostavno su se ljudi okrenili.

820
00:30:37,920 --> 00:30:40,300
 Da, nažalost su navikli veće na suze,

821
00:30:40,300 --> 00:30:42,300
 kod poroda djeca sa Downom sindromom,

822
00:30:42,300 --> 00:30:46,140
 pa što se sjeća glavna sestra, babica,

823
00:30:46,140 --> 00:30:50,520
 nakon što se djete opralo i sve ono što treba po samom rođenju.

824
00:30:51,180 --> 00:30:52,720
 Kad nam ga je ponovno došla pokazati,

825
00:30:52,720 --> 00:30:55,400
 znam da je bilo ono upitnik njoj nad glavom,

826
00:30:55,400 --> 00:30:58,400
 kao vi znate da djeti ima Downom sindromom.

827
00:30:58,400 --> 00:31:01,280
 Mi ono, znamo, ono, svi veseli, smijemo se.

828
00:31:01,280 --> 00:31:04,360
 I ono je bilo malo iznenađenje.

829
00:31:04,360 --> 00:31:06,760
 Stvarno njima je bilo iznenađenje pozitivno

830
00:31:06,760 --> 00:31:10,820
 i tako da, eto, od samog trenutka rođenja

831
00:31:10,820 --> 00:31:15,720
 je počeo mijenjati i svijest ljudi oko njih, za njih.

832
00:31:15,720 --> 00:31:18,520
 O kon sad ima godina?

833
00:31:19,580 --> 00:31:21,420
 Sada će tri u šesti mjesec.

834
00:31:21,420 --> 00:31:24,880
 A vidi se ga na potkama, na potkama je presladak.

835
00:31:24,880 --> 00:31:29,200
 Je, stvarno super napreduje.

836
00:31:29,200 --> 00:31:33,500
 Evo, potom sad uz brata njih dvoje zajedno rastu, napreduju.

837
00:31:33,500 --> 00:31:35,700
 Jedan drugom je oslavnac.

838
00:31:35,700 --> 00:31:40,220
 Jer djeca sa Downom sindromom,

839
00:31:40,220 --> 00:31:43,280
 mi nekad mislimo da su oni, imamo reć,

840
00:31:43,280 --> 00:31:45,260
 zakinuti za nešto,

841
00:31:45,260 --> 00:31:47,700
 a možda smo u stvari mi,

842
00:31:47,980 --> 00:31:51,560
 tako reć, normalni, zdravi ljudi,

843
00:31:51,560 --> 00:31:53,280
 ograničeni, jer

844
00:31:53,280 --> 00:31:56,320
 u njih je ljubav iskrena,

845
00:31:56,320 --> 00:31:58,220
 u njih je emocija, ona prava,

846
00:31:58,220 --> 00:32:00,220
 nema laganja, nema

847
00:32:00,220 --> 00:32:02,160
 pretvaranja, s njih u njih znate

848
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:02,980
 na čemu ste.

849
00:32:02,980 --> 00:32:05,360
 Tako da smatram da je to

850
00:32:05,360 --> 00:32:07,960
 najnije blagoslov nama,

851
00:32:07,960 --> 00:32:10,020
 jer, evo ja kao

852
00:32:10,020 --> 00:32:11,960
 momaka sa jednog razmišlja,

853
00:32:12,040 --> 00:32:13,520
 ono, jednog dana imat ću,

854
00:32:13,520 --> 00:32:15,280
 ako Bog da, ženu, djecu,

855
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:17,460
 kad bi nekad vidio neke roditelje

856
00:32:17,460 --> 00:32:19,160
 sa djecom s poteškoćama,

857
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:21,800
 znao bi reć, ono,

858
00:32:21,800 --> 00:32:23,000
 ajme Bože, ja to nikada ne mogu,

859
00:32:23,000 --> 00:32:24,660
 a koji što u životu nema mi to dat.

860
00:32:24,660 --> 00:32:26,380
 I Bog je baš to,

861
00:32:26,380 --> 00:32:29,840
 reka, ako misliš da je to baš ono što ne možeš,

862
00:32:29,840 --> 00:32:31,100
 da je to veće i od mene,

863
00:32:32,300 --> 00:32:33,160
 na kraju, eto,

864
00:32:33,160 --> 00:32:36,460
 promijenilo je nas sigurno kao dvojka osobe,

865
00:32:36,460 --> 00:32:38,520
 promijenilo je našu obitelj,

866
00:32:38,520 --> 00:32:39,300
 mijenja ljude,

867
00:32:39,300 --> 00:32:41,360
 baš, eto, ono,

868
00:32:41,360 --> 00:32:43,480
 zarazan, da rečem tako,

869
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:45,720
 svojom vedrinom, svojim veseljem,

870
00:32:45,720 --> 00:32:48,420
 tako da, vjerujem da će cilj život

871
00:32:48,420 --> 00:32:50,600
 mijenjati ljude oko sebe

872
00:32:50,600 --> 00:32:53,680
 i biti veliki osnovanac

873
00:32:53,680 --> 00:32:54,560
 i on i svom bratu,

874
00:32:54,560 --> 00:32:55,720
 a pogotovo brat njemu,

875
00:32:55,720 --> 00:32:57,360
 tako da,

876
00:32:57,360 --> 00:33:00,220
 bit će to jedna lijepa priča njihova.

877
00:33:02,220 --> 00:33:03,780
 i želio bih napomenuti,

878
00:33:03,780 --> 00:33:05,040
 znači, patera Iliju,

879
00:33:05,040 --> 00:33:08,040
 imali smo velikog,

880
00:33:08,040 --> 00:33:09,020
 većem tako,

881
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:11,380
 pomoć od,

882
00:33:11,380 --> 00:33:13,060
 znači, pater Ilija Grgić,

883
00:33:13,060 --> 00:33:14,640
 voditelj reda,

884
00:33:14,640 --> 00:33:16,160
 misjonara Krvi Kristove,

885
00:33:16,160 --> 00:33:17,640
 tu u Zagrebu,

886
00:33:17,640 --> 00:33:20,860
 on je bio s nama posebno umoliti,

887
00:33:20,860 --> 00:33:21,720
 znači,

888
00:33:21,720 --> 00:33:23,120
 prije ono što smo saznali,

889
00:33:23,120 --> 00:33:23,940
 početka, da,

890
00:33:23,940 --> 00:33:25,580
 prije ono što smo saznali da imamo problem,

891
00:33:25,580 --> 00:33:27,120
 zatim,

892
00:33:27,120 --> 00:33:29,040
 nakon što smo saznali,

893
00:33:29,040 --> 00:33:31,760
 dva navrata smo se ibaš i vidjeli,

894
00:33:32,140 --> 00:33:33,320
 kad je on bio u Splitu,

895
00:33:33,320 --> 00:33:35,940
 pa je u crkvi molio nad nama za nas,

896
00:33:35,940 --> 00:33:37,360
 i jedan put u Zagrebu,

897
00:33:37,360 --> 00:33:38,820
 on je isto znači,

898
00:33:38,820 --> 00:33:41,200
 a to je ono što vi s većenici,

899
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:42,600
 radite,

900
00:33:42,600 --> 00:33:43,120
 toliki,

901
00:33:43,120 --> 00:33:45,460
 osmijeh, on mir,

902
00:33:45,460 --> 00:33:46,300
 on nam uvijek govore,

903
00:33:46,300 --> 00:33:47,000
 bit će sve u redu,

904
00:33:47,000 --> 00:33:47,640
 ne brinite,

905
00:33:47,640 --> 00:33:48,340
 stvarno,

906
00:33:49,400 --> 00:33:51,080
 i onda imamo isto jednu anegdotu za,

907
00:33:51,080 --> 00:33:54,240
 kako je Dominik dobio u stvari ime,

908
00:33:54,240 --> 00:33:56,660
 jer mi smo cijeli život to sve,

909
00:33:56,660 --> 00:33:57,580
 od kad smo zajedno,

910
00:33:57,580 --> 00:33:58,080
 od kad smo,

911
00:33:58,080 --> 00:34:00,220
 kad sam opoznao njene roditelje,

912
00:34:00,220 --> 00:34:01,660
 pa smo mogli ih zajedno namjesu,

913
00:34:01,660 --> 00:34:05,660
 išli i dan danas u crkvu Svetog Dominika,

914
00:34:05,660 --> 00:34:07,040
 u Splitu na pazaru,

915
00:34:07,620 --> 00:34:10,400
 a oženili smo se na blagdan Svete Ane,

916
00:34:10,400 --> 00:34:12,200
 koja je zaštitnica obitelji.

917
00:34:12,200 --> 00:34:14,460
 Isto u crkvu Svetog Dominika.

918
00:34:14,460 --> 00:34:17,220
 Znači, Dominik Sveta Ana je bilo,

919
00:34:17,220 --> 00:34:20,020
 i ti si izrazila želju da,

920
00:34:20,020 --> 00:34:22,260
 ako bude dječak,

921
00:34:22,260 --> 00:34:23,200
 da bude Dominik,

922
00:34:23,200 --> 00:34:25,420
 a ako bude curica,

923
00:34:25,420 --> 00:34:28,140
 prvo od dva prijedloga koje smo imali,

924
00:34:28,140 --> 00:34:30,040
 je bilo da bude Ana,

925
00:34:30,040 --> 00:34:32,460
 i jednom priliku,

926
00:34:32,460 --> 00:34:33,920
 znači nakon te molitve,

927
00:34:33,920 --> 00:34:36,040
 ponovo, znači nama Pater Ilija,

928
00:34:36,040 --> 00:34:37,540
 sa smiješkom, ne brinite,

929
00:34:37,540 --> 00:34:38,440
 biće sve u redu,

930
00:34:38,440 --> 00:34:41,160
 molite se Svetoj Ani i Svetom Dominiku.

931
00:34:41,160 --> 00:34:42,580
 On nije znao,

932
00:34:42,580 --> 00:34:44,820
 znači, ne znao da idemo na mislu,

933
00:34:44,820 --> 00:34:46,460
 i da smo se ženili na Svetu Anu,

934
00:34:46,460 --> 00:34:47,000
 i da je to,

935
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:48,180
 znači ta dva imena,

936
00:34:48,180 --> 00:34:48,540
 izvojim,

937
00:34:48,540 --> 00:34:50,800
 mi smo se samo pogledali,

938
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:51,600
 i rekli to je to,

939
00:34:51,600 --> 00:34:52,640
 biće Dominik.

940
00:34:52,640 --> 00:34:55,960
 Krasno, krasno.

941
00:34:55,960 --> 00:35:00,000
 Stvarno, stvarno vam se divim,

942
00:35:00,000 --> 00:35:01,920
 ja svaku večer,

943
00:35:01,920 --> 00:35:02,840
 znači, da sam nasmijen,

944
00:35:02,840 --> 00:35:04,220
 ovdje postavljam pitanja sve,

945
00:35:04,220 --> 00:35:05,700
 ali već ja sam biste eksternik,

946
00:35:05,780 --> 00:35:06,660
 medla stoji u grlu,

947
00:35:06,660 --> 00:35:07,520
 slušajući vas,

948
00:35:07,520 --> 00:35:09,300
 i znači vam Bogu,

949
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:10,520
 jer on je stvarno,

950
00:35:10,520 --> 00:35:11,480
 bezlažen neki,

951
00:35:11,480 --> 00:35:14,960
 jer ja često i dobijam poruke,

952
00:35:14,960 --> 00:35:16,420
 ljudi koji ne mogu ostati trudni.

953
00:35:16,420 --> 00:35:19,280
 Neki dan sam imao jedan par,

954
00:35:19,280 --> 00:35:20,360
 koji su uletli onako,

955
00:35:20,360 --> 00:35:21,460
 znači,

956
00:35:21,460 --> 00:35:23,480
 pražit će samo mišljenje,

957
00:35:23,480 --> 00:35:24,880
 zapravo, oni su ni oženjeni,

958
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:26,580
 cura je ostalo slučajno trudna,

959
00:35:26,580 --> 00:35:28,780
 i ona želi roditi,

960
00:35:28,780 --> 00:35:30,480
 da čovjek praži sva prava.

961
00:35:30,480 --> 00:35:31,060
 Kaže,

962
00:35:31,060 --> 00:35:31,840
 gdje su moja prava,

963
00:35:31,840 --> 00:35:32,680
 to ako ja ne želim.

964
00:35:32,680 --> 00:35:32,960
 Dakle,

965
00:35:32,960 --> 00:35:35,420
 koliko negativnih priča slušam o tome,

966
00:35:35,420 --> 00:35:37,500
 i kad slučam vašu ljubavi,

967
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:40,260
 skupam se da ste ovo prihvatili,

968
00:35:40,260 --> 00:35:40,820
 ja,

969
00:35:40,820 --> 00:35:43,880
 samo da vam Bogu zakvaljim,

970
00:35:43,880 --> 00:35:44,560
 nasvima vama.

971
00:35:44,560 --> 00:35:46,720
 Hvala vama.

972
00:35:46,720 --> 00:35:49,880
 Nadam se da mladi ovo slušaju i pamte,

973
00:35:49,880 --> 00:35:52,620
 a možda sam posebno večas osvjetljiv,

974
00:35:52,620 --> 00:35:53,840
 možda to ne znaju mnogi,

975
00:35:53,840 --> 00:35:55,300
 da sam ja treba ubiti abortirati,

976
00:35:55,300 --> 00:35:55,660
 znaš.

977
00:35:55,660 --> 00:36:00,360
 Ja sam deveto djete obitelj,

978
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:02,460
 i normalno da u moj mjestu,

979
00:36:02,460 --> 00:36:04,560
 odakle ja dolazim,

980
00:36:04,560 --> 00:36:05,680
 imate devetero djece,

981
00:36:05,680 --> 00:36:06,840
 to već bilo previše,

982
00:36:06,840 --> 00:36:09,420
 ja da su moje mami svi savjetovali,

983
00:36:09,580 --> 00:36:10,640
 šta će ti deveto djete,

984
00:36:10,640 --> 00:36:11,480
 pobaci ga,

985
00:36:11,480 --> 00:36:13,680
 čak i bliža rodbina,

986
00:36:13,680 --> 00:36:14,440
 i tako dalje.

987
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:17,060
 I ona je tu uvijek prepričavala djete,

988
00:36:17,060 --> 00:36:18,780
 drago, ja sam samo vjerovala u Boga,

989
00:36:18,780 --> 00:36:21,580
 i vjerovala sam ako sam uspjela odhraniti,

990
00:36:21,580 --> 00:36:23,820
 osmjero djece odhraniti i tebe.

991
00:36:23,820 --> 00:36:28,020
 I moja mama je bila sama doma,

992
00:36:28,020 --> 00:36:30,240
 kad je dobila trudove,

993
00:36:30,240 --> 00:36:31,680
 znači to je bilo na selu,

994
00:36:31,680 --> 00:36:33,700
 u selu je tada umrla jedna žena,

995
00:36:33,700 --> 00:36:34,900
 svi su otčina s provod,

996
00:36:34,900 --> 00:36:36,520
 tata je bio na poslu,

997
00:36:36,520 --> 00:36:38,300
 starija djeca su bila u školi,

998
00:36:38,580 --> 00:36:40,640
 i tada nije bilo telefona i ostalo ga.

999
00:36:40,640 --> 00:36:42,300
 Znači, kaže ona,

1000
00:36:42,300 --> 00:36:43,380
 ja sam dobila trudove,

1001
00:36:43,380 --> 00:36:44,800
 i morala sam izabrat,

1002
00:36:44,800 --> 00:36:46,500
 moram te roditi,

1003
00:36:46,500 --> 00:36:47,180
 a sama sam.

1004
00:36:47,180 --> 00:36:49,940
 Kaže, osmjero djete sam rodila u bolnice,

1005
00:36:49,940 --> 00:36:51,340
 ali nijedno nisam rodila kod kuće,

1006
00:36:52,040 --> 00:36:54,600
 i nijedno djeto nisam morala sama pupak prevezati.

1007
00:36:54,600 --> 00:36:58,020
 Ali ona je uvijek isticela kako je o Bogu isto pomaguo sam.

1008
00:36:58,020 --> 00:36:58,600
 Ona kaže,

1009
00:36:58,600 --> 00:37:00,680
 djete, ja sam u jednu ruku uzela krunicu,

1010
00:37:00,680 --> 00:37:01,960
 molila krunicu,

1011
00:37:01,960 --> 00:37:05,140
 a u drugoj ruci sam pripremala toplu vodu da te mogu poroditi.

1012
00:37:05,140 --> 00:37:06,580
 I onda kaže,

1013
00:37:06,580 --> 00:37:10,160
 od svega mi je bilo najteže to presići pupčanu vrbicu,

1014
00:37:10,160 --> 00:37:11,200
 jer nijednom djetu nisam,

1015
00:37:11,200 --> 00:37:14,040
 samo sebi moram prevezati pupčanu vrbicu,

1016
00:37:14,720 --> 00:37:18,340
 i nijednom djetu nisam nikada vezala pupak

1017
00:37:18,340 --> 00:37:19,400
 i ne znam kako se to radi,

1018
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:20,820
 kaže, ali ne mogu pust da umreš.

1019
00:37:20,820 --> 00:37:23,960
 A sad, možete mi sam iskala to snaga,

1020
00:37:23,960 --> 00:37:24,820
 da si sam doma,

1021
00:37:24,820 --> 00:37:25,560
 da rodiš djeta,

1022
00:37:25,560 --> 00:37:27,240
 te sjećaš pupčanu vrbicu i sve.

1023
00:37:27,240 --> 00:37:29,500
 Dakle, uvijek sam slušao te njezine riječi,

1024
00:37:29,500 --> 00:37:30,340
 kak je to pričala.

1025
00:37:30,340 --> 00:37:31,420
 Ona nikad, nikada,

1026
00:37:31,420 --> 00:37:33,360
 nikoga nije osuđivala isto od sve,

1027
00:37:33,360 --> 00:37:36,120
 onaj rodbinu i sve one koje su inagovarali da me povaci.

1028
00:37:36,120 --> 00:37:38,240
 Važno je da ih nije nikada slušala.

1029
00:37:39,500 --> 00:37:41,460
 Ja sam mojeg slušao te njezine riječi,

1030
00:37:41,460 --> 00:37:43,840
 nikad nisam pričao tome nikdje javno,

1031
00:37:43,840 --> 00:37:45,240
 nikad ništa nisam govorio,

1032
00:37:45,240 --> 00:37:48,060
 dok nisam došao na,

1033
00:37:48,060 --> 00:37:49,700
 imao mladu misu.

1034
00:37:49,700 --> 00:37:51,780
 Znači, mlada misa vam je to kad se radi

1035
00:37:51,780 --> 00:37:52,920
 u tvojom rodnom kraju,

1036
00:37:52,920 --> 00:37:54,300
 nakon što postaneš svećenik

1037
00:37:54,300 --> 00:37:56,800
 i na kraju mlade mise imaš zahvalni govor.

1038
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:59,800
 Ja sam ga pripremio večeras ovde da čujete,

1039
00:37:59,800 --> 00:38:01,520
 tada je bila prihoda,

1040
00:38:01,520 --> 00:38:03,540
 zahvalim svojom mami što me nije pobacilo,

1041
00:38:03,540 --> 00:38:04,480
 što sam oslo živ.

1042
00:38:04,480 --> 00:38:06,320
 Pa evo, to je minuto,

1043
00:38:06,380 --> 00:38:08,000
 ja ću samo krenuti prema mojom laptopu,

1044
00:38:08,000 --> 00:38:08,620
 vi oznanite.

1045
00:38:08,620 --> 00:38:10,380
 Pa ćemo se mi vratiti poslije,

1046
00:38:10,380 --> 00:38:14,560
 samo da poslušate taj dio.

1047
00:38:14,560 --> 00:38:21,660
 Možda će malo odjekivati,

1048
00:38:21,660 --> 00:38:23,080
 ali nadam se ćete čuti sve dobro.

1049
00:38:24,380 --> 00:38:26,760
 Znači da se mi vrlo Boga.

1050
00:38:26,760 --> 00:38:29,380
 I zato, to što vas,

1051
00:38:29,380 --> 00:38:31,140
 kao svećenik svojim pred vama,

1052
00:38:31,140 --> 00:38:32,840
 zaista zbom milost,

1053
00:38:32,840 --> 00:38:35,900
 upućujem i zahvalim Bogu,

1054
00:38:35,900 --> 00:38:38,360
 jer se, kao kaželjstvo mnista,

1055
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:41,280
 odpostavite komunist mladosti.

1056
00:38:41,280 --> 00:38:43,980
 Na drugom mjestu,

1057
00:38:43,980 --> 00:38:46,940
 želim zahvaliti svoje blake.

1058
00:38:48,380 --> 00:38:49,380
 Hvala što si vrlo Boga.

